# Canonical author identities.
#
# Collapses alternate names/emails that appear in history under a single
# identity so `git log`, `git shortlog -sne`, and GitHub's contributor views
# show one person. Format:
#   Proper Name <proper@email> <other@email>
#   Proper Name <proper@email> Other Name <other@email>

